sigmavault-desktop (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of SigmaVault Desktop UI
  * Dashboard with system metrics and compression statistics
  * Job management interface with filtering and detail views
  * Storage management for disks, pools, datasets, and shares
  * Agent swarm monitoring with real-time metrics
  * System settings for network, services, and notifications
  * Modern GTK4 + libadwaita interface
  * Auto-refresh with configurable intervals (5-20s)
  * 5 fully-integrated views covering entire API surface
  * Comprehensive error handling and logging
  * Responsive design for narrow and wide screens

 -- SigmaVault Project <dev@sigmavault.example.com>  Sat, 08 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000
